x = torch.tensor([[1.0, 2.0], [3.0, 4.0]], dtype=torch.float64, device=
    torch.device('cpu'))
expected_json = {'__type': 'Tensor', 'value': [[1.0, 2.0], [3.0, 4.0]],
    'dtype': {'__type': 'torch_dtype', 'value': 'torch.float64'}, 'device':
    {'__type': 'torch_device', 'value': 'cpu'}}
